HEADWORD: Bleareye
<hw>Blear"eye`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A disease of the eyelids, consisting in chronic inflammation of the
margins, with a gummy secretion of sebaceous matter.</def>
<rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Blear-eyed</ent>⟦br⟧
